DESCRIPTION
-----------
This is an Xcode (4, but written to support 3) project of an iOS (iPhone/iPod Touch/iPad) project that implements a native app of the popular NA Cleantime Calculator (NACC), which is a JavaScript-based Web app available here:

    http://magshare.org/blog/nacc-the-na-cleantime-calculator/

The concept is simple: Enter your cleandate, and a congratulatory message will be displayed, along with a scrolling "KeyTag Chain." If the date is an anniversary, then congratulations are in order, and the app is delighted to say so.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
This is an iOS app, made for iPhones and iPads. It is only available via the Apple App Store, and is free.

    http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/nacc/id452299196?ls=1&mt=8

The code in this repository was developed on Apple Xcode 4.0.2, on a Mac running 10.6.8. It *should* work on somewhat older version of Xcode and the OS.

The spec uses Omni Group OmniGraffle. It's cool. Get it here:

    http://www.omnigroup.com/products/omnigraffle/

INSTALLATION
------------
Get it from the App Store.
Get the code and spec from here.

